<HEADLINE> Lineup for Sunday TV News Shows  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   Lineup for the Sunday TV news shows:
<TEXT>
<P>
   ABC's ''This Week'' -- Topics: Nuclear security, the Republican
agenda and the Gore campaign. Guests: Energy Secretary Bill
Richardson; Senate Majority Leader Trent Lott, R-Miss.; and William
Daley, incoming chairman of Gore 2000 campaign.
