he was indicted, and was immediately released on bond.
</P>
<P>
   The 38-year-old singer is facing 12 counts of fraudulently
obtaining the prescription drug hydrocodone, a sedative similar to
codeine. He has said he got addicted to hydrocodone after it was
prescribed to him as pain medication for an injury.
</P>
