<TEXT>
<P>
	   LAKE LUZERNE, N.Y. (AP) - A 35-year-old man died late Friday,
several hours after crashing his all-terrain vehicle into a car,
police said.
</P>
<P>
   Police in Warren County said Kevin J. Garnsey was riding his ATV
in front of his Lake Luzerne home when he collided with a car
driven by Scott Bujanowski, 30, of Saratoga County.
</P>
